				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6d31266 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6d31266" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<p> </p><p style="line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">政府大力推動數位</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">ｅ</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">化的政策與日月異的科技技術發展，會計帳務處理從紙本憑證搭配手記帳的形式，至電腦系統入帳，再高速推進全面數位化的時代</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">。</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">根據財政部資料，2022 年全國電子發票佔發票種類使用率比率以突破八成，會計資訊處裡工作模式已正式踏入全新的階段，透過奇勝資訊的憑證ｅ化系統，能大幅優化帳務數位化效率，流暢的將資料拋轉至各項系統</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">。</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">奇勝於 2017 年推出</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">憑證ｅ化系統至今，已協助超過 300 家以上之會計師、記帳士事務所導入，得到正面的肯定反饋，認為已有效減降事務所同仁資料處理的作業時間</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">。</span></p><p style="line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); color: #ff0000;"><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">憑證</span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;">ｅ</span></span><span style="color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">化系統</span>適用於會計師事務所、記帳士事務所、公司企業之會計帳務運用，如有興趣歡迎填寫<span style="text-decoration-line: underline;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc8m-Dp-fhXfCROGOGlb_dk-LAo_OvT5RAOriL89txUr5NEtg/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">線上詢價單</a></span></span>或來電各區業務諮詢。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: '微軟正黑體',sans-serif;">台北區業務　<span lang="EN-US">02-22577401#319</span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">台中區業務　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">04-23202807#30</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: '微軟正黑體',sans-serif;">台南區業務　<span lang="EN-US">06-2006219#20</span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: '微軟正黑體',sans-serif;"><span lang="EN-US">高</span></span><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">雄區業務　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );">07-3805919</span></p><p style="line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 18.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;"> </span></p>						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
							</div>
		</section>
							</div>〈<a href="https://www.hserp.tw/wordpress/2023/03/17/112cpa/">會計師全聯會系統分享交流座談會幕後花絮</a>〉這篇文章最早發佈於《<a href="https://www.hserp.tw/wordpress">奇勝資訊</a>》。]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
