		<item>
		<title>憑證 e 化 &#8211; 彙總傳票『新增』快速掃描建檔</title>
		<link>https://www.hserp.tw/wordpress/2020/08/03/%e6%86%91%e8%ad%89-e-%e5%8c%96-2-2-%e7%89%88-%e3%80%8e%e6%96%b0%e5%a2%9e%e3%80%8f-%e5%bf%ab%e9%80%9f%e6%8e%83%e6%8f%8f%e5%bb%ba%e6%aa%94/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[lin judy]]></dc:creator>
